========
 IGNORE 
========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
:doc created at: Sun Jan  4 21:10:36 2009
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

ignore users for a certain time

| 

  register all .py files 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *ignore*

    :description: ignore <nick> <seconds> .. ignore <nick> for <seconds>

    :permissions: OPER .. IGNORE

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !ignore dunker 3600
        <output> ignoring dunker for 3600 seconds


2) *ignore-del*

    :description: ignore-del <nick> .. unignore <nick>

    :permissions: OPER .. IGNORE

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !ignore-del dunker
        <output> ignore for dunker removed


3) *ignore-list*

    :description: show ignore list

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !ignore-list
        <output> {}


